casebody.data:
David Ezell SIMPSON
v.
Sheriff MCFADDEN State of North Carolina No. 194P19-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2019 David Ezell Simpson, for Simpson, David Ezell. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, R. Andrew Murray, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 10th of June 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Mecklenburg County:

"Dismissed without prejudice by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th of June 2019."
